These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, go, backgammon
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
City: hamburg, marseilles, miami, london
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##8
 3. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##8
 6. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person playing backgammon is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person traveling to london is the person playing go##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person playing go is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person traveling to miami##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Game   | poker | backgammon   | monopoly   | go  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| City     | hamburg    | miami | marseilles     | london    |

