.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
House: tower, palace, colonial, cottage
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, aristoff, fonseca, old-henry
 1. the fan of salsa is between the vegafina-smoker and the fan of indie##2
 2. the palace house is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8
 3. the palace house is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the tower house is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 5. the vegafina-smoker is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the cottage house##8
 7. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
 8. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
11. the vegafina-smoker is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the cottage house is on the left of the palace house##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the tower house is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the tower house is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8
19. the cottage house is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| House      | tower | colonial | cottage  | palace  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Cigar           | fonseca | old-henry | vegafina    | aristoff  |

