The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
City: miami, nizza, edinburgh, boston
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the blend-smoker is the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar      | prince   | dunhill     | blend    | fonseca |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| City         | miami | edinburgh  | boston     | nizza  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

