The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, roller, subway
 1. the person playing chess is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
 3. the person playing canasta is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the person who's birthday is in may##7
11. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
